def get_unique_elements(my_list):
    """
    Returns all unique elements in a list.
    """
    seen = set()
    return [x for x in my_list if x not in seen and not seen.add(x)]

def get_duplicate_elements(my_list):
    """

    """
    seen = set()
    duplicates = []
